        "Active incident declaration — MDR Complete customers trigger dedicated Incident Response Lead assignment for a confirmed compromise or active breach scenario",
        "Proactive customer escalation — customers can initiate contact when they have observed suspicious activity themselves and want immediate analyst involvement",
