      action:"Open the Firewall Management Dashboard. Show the fleet health overview and point out the sync status column. Click into a specific firewall and show its individual health summary. Show the active alert section and explain what types of alerts surface here — firmware, configuration, and connectivity. Ask the customer how many firewalls they are currently managing and how they track their health."
