    "CTO / CISO":["What is your current network security architecture — and how does it handle the encrypted traffic that accounts for over 90% of network flows today?", "How quickly can you contain a confirmed network compromise — automated network isolation or a manual multi-step process?", "Are your firewall appliances current on firmware — and what is your process for emergency patching when a critical CVE is disclosed?", "How are you demonstrating network segmentation and perimeter control effectiveness to your board, insurer, or auditors?", "What is the refresh cycle on your current firewall hardware — and are you planning to consolidate vendor relationships?"],
    "MSP / Partner SE":["Are you managing firewalls across your customer base from a single management console or connecting to each customer's device independently?", "What is your process for firewall firmware updates across your customer estate — and how long does a critical patch take to deploy fleet-wide?", "Are your customers asking about SD-WAN to optimise their multi-site connectivity and WAN spend?", "How are you handling firewall-to-endpoint Synchronized Security — is this something you are offering as part of your managed service?", "What is your current support overhead for multi-site firewall management — and what would centralised orchestration from Sophos Central save?"],
