      action:"Navigate to Cases. Open an existing case and walk through the detection timeline — show how multiple related detections from different sources are correlated into one investigation. Show the analyst notes section and the evidence attachments. Walk through the MITRE ATT&CK heat map for the case showing which tactics were involved. Show the response action log and explain what it means for compliance and insurance documentation."
