      talk:"\"The Threat Analysis Center marked as Classic is relevant context for customers coming from the Sophos XDR side of the business. Existing Sophos Central customers who used Threat Analysis Center for their EDR and XDR investigations will find that interface preserved as the Classic view in the unified Sophos and Taegis platform. The Detections, Cases, and Live Discover workflows they are familiar with are all still here. What the Taegis platform adds on top is the broader Data Lake, the CTU detection rule library, the 350-plus integrations, and the Security Operations capabilities that go well beyond what the original Sophos XDR Threat Analysis Center provided. For customers in the Sophos-to-Taegis migration journey, Classic is the bridge.\"",
