      action:"Walk through the Dashboard widgets. Point out the engine breakdown and explain what each engine is catching. Click into a specific detection category to drill down into the detail. Show the east-west versus north-south split and explain why growing east-west activity is a lateral movement indicator. Ask the customer whether their current network security tooling differentiates between internal east-west threats and perimeter north-south threats."
