      talk:"\"The Overview Beta gives you the strategic view that sits above the operational Dashboard. While the Dashboard shows you what is happening right now, the Overview shows you what has been happening over weeks and months — which threat categories are trending upward, which devices are repeatedly appearing in detections and represent persistent risk, and how the five detection engines are performing relative to each other. For a CISO or security manager who needs to report on network security posture trends rather than investigate specific incidents, the Overview is the right screen. It is in Beta but already provides the longitudinal view that operational teams use for programme performance reporting.\"",
