      talk:"\"NDR Reports — currently in Beta — give you the structured reporting output that security governance and compliance teams need. Network threat detection at the technical level is detailed and operational. What a CISO, board member, or external auditor needs is a summarised view: what was detected on the network this month, what are the trending threat types, how many high-severity network threats were identified and investigated. The NDR report provides that structured summary automatically, without requiring an analyst to manually compile detection logs. Scheduled monthly delivery means the reporting obligation is met consistently without manual effort.\"",
