      talk:"\"Mobile is one of the highest-risk attack surfaces in most organisations — and consistently one of the most underprotected. Every employee has a smartphone accessing corporate email, Teams, SharePoint, and sometimes VPN. Yet in most environments those devices have no security software beyond what the OS ships with. The Dashboard gives you the full picture immediately: how many devices are managed, how many are compliant, and what threats have been detected. Mobile threats are a completely different category from endpoint threats — malicious apps, Wi-Fi man-in-the-middle attacks, and OS-level exploits. None of those are caught by your endpoint protection tools.\"",
