      action:"Navigate to Devices. Filter to non-compliant devices and click one to show the specific compliance failure reason. Show a BYOD enrolled device versus a corporate device and explain the different remote actions available. Demonstrate the remote lock action and explain how it differs from a full wipe. Show the last check-in timestamp and explain what an extended absence indicates."
