        "Dynamic group assignment — devices automatically assigned to the correct group based on platform, ownership type, OS version, or enrollment method",
        "Separation of BYOD and corporate — different groups enforce different policy strictness; BYOD groups have privacy-respecting limits on what MDM can see",
        "Department or role-based groups — field workers, executives, contractors, and standard employees each have distinct app and security requirements"
