      talk:"\"Task Bundles solve the new device onboarding problem at scale. When a new employee gets a corporate iPhone, instead of manually pushing 8 separate policies and 12 apps one at a time, you apply one Task Bundle and every policy, every app, every configuration profile deploys in a single action. The device is fully configured for that employee's role in minutes. For IT teams managing hundreds of devices, this is the operational efficiency that makes MDM sustainable — you define the bundle once for each device profile and apply it consistently every time without checking a manual checklist.\"",
