    {q:"Sophos switches are newer — are they enterprise-ready?",a:"Sophos Switches support the full enterprise switching feature set: 802.1X, LACP, spanning tree, VLAN, QoS, PoE+, and PoE++. The differentiation is cloud management and Sophos Central integration. For high-complexity enterprise environments needing Cisco-level feature depth, Catalyst remains strong. For mid-market organizations wanting integrated management at lower TCO, Sophos Switches deliver the right capability."}
